12);\n}\n}\n\n</style><br><hr><br>\n\n\n<div id=\"image-grid\"></div>\n\n\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\"\nhref=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lightbox2/2.11.4/css/lightbox.min.css\">\n\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lightbox2/2.11.4/js/lightbox.min.js\"></script>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tesseract.js@5/dist/tesseract.min.js\"></script>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"source-images\" style=\"display:none;\">\n  \n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"320\" data-original-height=\"1280\" data-original-width=\"606\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhzMzvW4T2bpYwq-DTLS8_XbfMmyDNV3BuB1jj9qYdKpioQN47-KLn0RuGwFkuBp56fY-380u9ZYrHTD_ZvXER8TXAZ8SFoVy6-NrQx-nOJ2yoJZBDEAgm0JqhwaEH0x2M4cQjS1pbyWyOAphbBlOwC5H7SsBx17lhNjfj-Nxz4IYzH6ZEKCMxO-45cbfg/s320/IMG-20210722-WA0000.jpg\"/></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"320\" data-original-height=\"1280\" data-original-width=\"606\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhBcMRVcWLmYNp_YGT9oDOnVwOyilD5vqvwquqNTT8Jg_zLBnHilGMMwMECA0NHAblWNAtMDNjz156GAY9GmlfvVim8QcFX_nd_4ZzePCNdJRZm66KYzQ1fSollOW_wbvOe-D7t1jPyy8x2fPl4oh2eo49Dh8naDq2HAd59bsuIBpnXt0sz7TUFY5ZjVrw/s320/IMG-20210722-WA0001.jpg\"/></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"320\" data-original-height=\"1280\" data-original-width=\"606\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgnswaqpyjGhFzdsS22lracPOXOmziYCQQ4n5mDfd-ms842Vp1pUJgDkd2h_TKE3hGn3Ku2TcfKCvCQXlOMkytbT-dIyiSRaDBZouzOkR8NN7PKdWGFI-aEFRO0fzoBNmGhrPj2gdVyyEgjaPguodwDmZZKAEY1PNVbA3xlyTU_pQKahI3_-zyLL5O44tQ/s320/IMG-20210722-WA0002.jpg\"/></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"320\" data-original-height=\"1280\" data-original-width=\"606\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi9vUB2QF9cSx